---
title: Creamy Chicken, Citrus and Courgette Rigatoni with Garlicky Greens and Creme Fraiche
description: Get your greens in with our Creamy Chicken, Citrus and Courgette Rigatoni. A simple creamy sauce ties together the zesty steam-fried veg with pasta perfectly suited to carry all the sauce - delicious!
